attributes.name: Moderation in production
attributes.title: Moderation in production
attributes.description:
Cotton mostly grown in Colombia to make the textile 
Textil made in Medellin 
Garment manufactured in Medellin
Washing in Medellin at a Laundry with a private water treatment plant recycling over 70% of the water and cleaning the rest to feed it back to the main river of Medellin cleaner than what it was received.
